Select the physical aspects of your character's body.  This is broken
down into two basic catagories - frame and height - and will be used for
sizing the various equipment found in the game.  Size will also be used
for determining modifiers to your character, such as weight. Please type
the height and frame on one line, using the list below.
  
    Height: Tiny/Short/Average/Tall/Giant
    Frame: Feather/Scant/Light/Medium/Heavy/Massive/Mammoth


